quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,(Ndifunga ngeNtaba) yeTûr
  52,2,NangeNcwadi ebhaliweyo
  52,3,Kumacwecwe avulwe ondlalwa
  52,4,NangoMzi1 ohanjelwa rhoqo
  52,5,Nangophahla (izulu) oluphakamele phezulu
  52,6,Nangolwandle oluzele (ngumlilo)
  52,7,Inene isohlwayo seNkosi yakho siza kwenzeka
  52,8,Ngokuba akukho mthinteli (waso)
  52,9,NgeMini izulu liya kuzamazama ngokujikelezayo
  52,10,Neentaba zigqithe zimke
  52,11,Yeha ke ngalooMini kubaphiki
  52,12,Abancokola amampunge bezonwabisa
  52,13,Ngemini abaya kutshovelwa eMlilweni wesiHogo ngamandla
  52,14,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Nangu ke lo Mlilo naniwuphika"
  52,15,"Ngumlingo na lo, okanye aniboni"
  52,16,(Ngenani ke) nitshe phakathi apho; yibani nomonde okanye ningabi namonde kuyafana kuni. Nihlawulwa ngoko nakwenzayo kuphela
  52,17,Inene amalungisa aya kuba semiyezweni naselonwabeni
  52,18,"Esonwabela oko iNkosi yawo Iwanike kona, Ibe neNkosi yawo Iwakhusele esohlwayweni soMlilo wesiHogo"
  52,19,"(Kuya kuthiwa kwabakholwayo): “Yidlani, nisele, naneliseke ngenxa yoko nakwenzayo.”"
  52,20,"Baya kuba bengqiyamile ezitroneni ezidwelisiweyo, kananjalo Siya kubatshatisa neembelukazi zabafazi abanamehlo amakhulu (amahle)"
  52,21,"Abo baya bakholwa abantwana babo balandela ekhondweni labo ngokholo Siya kubadibanisa nenzala yabo, kwaye aSiyi kubabandeza nto kwizinto zabo. Umntu ngamnye awakusebenzelayo kugciniwe"
  52,22,Kananjalo Siya kubapha iziqhamo nenyama nantoni na abaya kuyinqwenela
  52,23,Baya kunikana indebe (yewayini) apho akuyi kubakho ntetho imbi nakwenziwa kwasono
  52,24,Kuya kuhamba hamba phakathi kwabo (izicaka) ezingamakhwenkwana azele ukulungiselela bona engathi ziiperile ezilondoloziweyo
  52,25,Ke kaloku baya kusondelana babuzane
  52,26,"Baya kuthi: “Inene thina kwixesha elidlulileyo esasikunye nabantu bakuthi ngalo sasisoyika (ukumenza umsindo uAllâh)"
  52,27,"Waza uAllâh Wasibonelela ngobuBele baKhe, Wasikhusela kananjalo kwisohlwayo soMlilo otshisayo"
  52,28,"Inene sasidla ngokucela kuYe ngaphambili. Inene, nguYe OnguMncedi, uSozinceba"